mI tE wApralyAs टrEडaऑP kAya AhE naPA kAya toटA AhE 
tumhI samjUn घEणyApAsUn duwyAcE mUlyamApan Aणi डiJAin karaणyAkडE wAटcAl karat AhAt 
ठIk AhE 
punhA joparyaqt nEटwarkacA saqbaqध AhE toparyaqt tumhI ऑpटikal kamyunikEशnasAठI nEटwark टopolऑjI samjAwUn sAqgaणyAs sakषam asAwE 
mI AधI mhaटalyApramAणE tE hom liqkawar PAybar AhE kI kor nEटwark AhE yAwar awalaqbUn AhE 
jar hE mEटro nEटwark asEl tar koणatyA prakArcI टopolऑjI wAparlI pAhijE Aणi tyAcE wiशlEषaण dEखIl karA 
AmhI niषkriya ऑpटikal nEटwarkawar थoडA tAण dEU 
kAraण tE asE nEटwark AhEt jE Aj moठyA pramAणAwar tऐnAt kElE jAणAr AhEt 
hE muखya nEटwark nAhI tE niषkriya ऑpटikal liqks AhEt jE moठyA pramAणAwar tऐnAt kElE jAणAr AhEt 
tyAmuളE sarwAt jAst pramAणAt PAybar wAyralEs kamyunikEशanlA samarथan dEणyAsAठI tऐnAt kElE jAणAr AhE 
Aणi tE sarwa parasparasaqwAdI duwE AhEt AdarशapणE duwE pAs karणE Awaशyak AhE 
tar AmhI iqडakटiwh ऑpटikal liqkacE kAryapradarशan mEटriks kAya AhEt yAbaddal थoडE aधik tapशIlAt jAU tyAmuളE hA शikaणyAcA pariणAm AhE 
